attributes.Long form description: The student's task is to disassemble the IKEA KNAVERRIK table, so he starts by systematically unscrewing the first 4 hex socket heads of the top table with an Allen wrench, then unscrewing the head socket heads of the shelf, then he arranges the furniture in different positions to unscrew the remaining 4 screws of the top table. Once the student unscrewed all the screws from the top table, he disassembles the top table from the legs and place it on the work table. Then, after this is done, unscrew the screws of the shelf legs to disassemble it leg by leg. Once the student finishes disassembling each leg, he places on the table the shelf.
